        <Parent_String>sinks (fixtures) [300052634], plumbing fixtures [300052575], plumbing and stormwater system components [300052523], system components [300242031], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
